snippet.title: Octopus 21 Game [ GX4000 _ Amstrad CPC+] FINAL Version shown at #RGC2023 18 & 19 November 2023
snippet.description:
Octopus _ New game for Amstrad GX4000 and CPC+
Oldschool design & graphics as Game & Watch classic game "Octopus" adaptation for Amstrad.

RELEASE DATE : Saturday 25th of November 2023 (9h00)
On Gamejolt link : https://gamejolt.com/games/Octopus21/856388

Game info:
1 & 2 player mode 
Hi score saving
Game end scene 

Staff et credits:

Screens and GFX : EDDO (Ripped GW Gallery 4) & Cyrille Ayor61
Musics : SuTeKH / EpyteoR
Code : Cyrille "Ayor61" Gouret    (GGP)

Music Credits : All done by SuTeKH / EpyteoR
T.D.K.-Knockerboys
Mike-Gibs-Donkey-Kong-Country-Aquatic-Ambience
SuTeKH-Egyptian-Slow-Dance

Final Version.

Final GX4000 / CPC+ Cartridge Octopus 21 version :
Release very soon on Ayor61 GameJolt page .

More info on Amstradiens Facebook group :
https://www.facebook.com/groups/amstradiens/?ref=share
